He hasn't mentioned it.

104
00:06:24,080 --> 00:06:25,440
You know, boys

105
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,840
are not like girls.

106
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,760
It's better to have daughters,

107
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,760
as they tell their moms everything.

108
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:34,120
Boys are not as sensitive as girls.

109
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,520
You have to ask him directly.

110
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,840
It's better to ask you.

111
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:39,460
Let's add each other on WeChat, shall we?

112
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:40,400
I'm planning to

113
