124
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:55,680
That's it.

125
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,400
Got it.

126
00:06:56,400 --> 00:06:57,840
Practice makes perfect.

127
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,280
Try it yourself.

128
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:00,200
The customers are done eating.

129
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,600
Go clean the table, please.

130
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:02,200
OK.

131
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:08,680
Two cups of latte, please.

132
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,120
OK.

