Latte.

136
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,400
And a sandwich set meal.

137
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:23,480
OK. A sandwich set meal.

138
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,210
Please bear with me.

139
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,840
Sandwich set meal.

140
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,720
72 yuan in total, please.

141
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,760
You can pay by scanning the code.

142
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,980
WeChat code scanning.

143
