Why did you take a picture of me?

144
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:54,200
I wanted to send it to Ling Xiao,

145
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:55,800
and let him know that you've completed your first transaction.

146
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,400
Do I look nice in the picture?

147
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,960
My facial expression wasn't good enough.

148
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:01,020
Add a filter before you send it to him.

149
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,120
Two cups of latte, right?

150
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,520
Make a sandwich set meal.

151
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,160
Got it.

152
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:22,320
So you've done this only as a hobby, right?

153
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:24,780
Yes, I've never systematically learned it.

154
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:26,640
But I really like it.

155
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:27,120
So

156
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,920
I learned it by watching videos.

157
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,720
OK, I got it.

158
00:08:32,909 --> 00:08:33,669
You may leave now.

159
00:08:33,669 --> 00:08:34,730
We'll consider it.

160
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,549
Alright, bye.

161
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:38,520
Bye.

162
00:08:41,549 --> 00:08:43,880
She didn't seem to know what she was doing.

163
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,680
No, no, no.

164
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:49,880
Please keep my CV. I'm back for my bag.

165
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,720
OK, OK, OK.

166
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,480
See you later.

