00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,240
See you later.

168
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:55,040
See you later.

169
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,400
What do you think of her?

170
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,320
Quite cute.

171
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:02,960
But there is one thing about her that's not ideal.

172
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,640
She can't even polish a bead.

173
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:06,360
That said,

174
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,120
there's something about her

175
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,320
that I really like.

176
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:09,280
What is it?

177
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,400
She is a girl.

178
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,840
A girl?

179
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,560
What do we need a girl for?

180
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,360
So that you can be distracted from your relationship.

181
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,000
You...

182
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,360
Stop teasing me.

183
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,520
I already have Miao now,

184
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,240
don't I?

185
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,480
Let me tell you something.

186
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,960
Recently, Miao has been treating me very well.

187
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,280
He'd stay up late

188
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,280
to finish all my work.

189
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,440
He told me

190
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:32,400
girls shouldn't stay up late,

191
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,160
especially when

192
00:09:33,160 --> 00:09:34,480
they're over 25 years old.

193
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,560
Girls must take good care of themselves.

194
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,520
He also said

195
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,600
he'll do everything

196
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,330
that requires staying up late.

197
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,480
She looked the part.

198
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,480
Not bad.

199
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:51,240
As least she has something to do

200
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,320
in He Ziqiu's shop.

201
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,720
But don't forget to remind her

202
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,640
of her summer holiday homework.

203
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,080
Sorry, it's my fault.

204
00:10:07,680 --> 00:10:08,440
I should have

205
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,880
talked to you in advance.

206
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,400
I thought

207
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,200
you'd be happy about

208
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,480
our return.

209
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,520
When will my aunt arrive?

210
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,780
She arrived in the afternoon,

211
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,880
and helped me with some shopping

212
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,540
as well as sorting things out.

213
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:26,720
Can I help?

214
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,720
No, thanks.

215
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,360
You're very busy at work.

216
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,800
Just focus on your job.

217
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,320
I know

218
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,800
Chengzi and I

219
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,520
have made things difficult for you.

220
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,040
Can you stop

221
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,200
talking about this?

222
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:46,240
What do you want me to say?

223
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,520
Nothing.

224
00:10:50,680 --> 00:10:51,400
I just

225
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:53,280
want to settle down here.

226
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:54,410
That's fine with me.

227
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,720
You're always like this.

228
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:01,480
Whatever's in your heart,

229
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,840
just say it.

230
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:04,840
You didn't tell me

231
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,500
you were coming back, either.

232
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,040
What's more, you lied to me,

233
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,520
saying you came back to see your dad.

234
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:11,980
But it turned out you had already found a job.

235
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:15,600
I just don't understand

236
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,240
why you wouldn't

237
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:18,840
tell me how you feel.

238
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,720
What are you thinking about right now?

239
00:11:20,720 --> 00:11:21,920
Just tell me.

240
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,880
I want to marry Jianjian.

241
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:34,880
Isn't it too hasty?

242
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:39,020
Of course, this is your own business.

243
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:41,740
Whatever you decide to do,

244
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:43,400
I'll support you.

245
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,480
But I just think that

246
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,600
at the moment,

247
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,160
you have neither a flat nor a car,

248
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,480
once you're married,

249
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,210
where are you two going to live?

250
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,240
How about this?

251
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:59,280
I'll sell my flat in Singapore

252
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,680
next year,

253
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:03,400
and buy you a big flat here.

254
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,820
At least you'll have a place to call home.

255
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,840
I just want to arrange everything

256
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:11,240
I can for you,

257
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:14,600
so that your life can be easier.

258
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:28,120
Dad, what brought you here?

259
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,360
I called you,

260
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,620
but you didn't answer.

261
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,730
Are you busy?

262
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:34,040
Yes.

263
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:35,000
There's a new intern

264
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,480
in our office.

265
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:39,120
Why didn't you answer my call?

266
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,880
Was it because mom wouldn't allow you to

267
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:43,480
or you were not happy for me

268
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,760
to go to Beijing?

269
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:45,520
Beijing?

270
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,780
Oh, your transfer.

271
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:50,320
Didn't mom tell you?

272
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,960
I've been staying in a hotel recently,

273
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,840
so I haven't met her.

274
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,520
Why are you staying in a hotel?

275
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,920
Tell me about your transfer

276
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:01,960
to Beijing.

277
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:03,720
I'm going to Beijing

278
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,840
because our TV station

279
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,800
has set up an office in Beijing.

280
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:06,760
My boss needs two people to go with him.

281
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:08,160
I'll be back in two years.

282
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,090
Dad, what's the matter?

283
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,080
Good.

284
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:15,600
Since your mom and I are going to get divorced,

285
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,200
it's good for you to stay away.

286
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,720
Otherwise, she may bother you every day,

287
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,840
because she can't bother me anymore.

288
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,920
Divorce?

289
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,300
You two are going to get divorced?

290
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,800
I can't stand it anymore.

