00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:49,140
No problem.

864
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:52,210
Have some watermelon, please.

865
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:54,000
I don't like watermelon.

866
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:54,800
If you're busy,

867
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,130
just feel free to leave.

868
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:57,760
You don't have to take care of us.

869
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:58,840
What would you like to eat?

870
00:35:58,840 --> 00:35:59,800
I'll get them for you.

871
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:00,800
No, thanks.

872
