877
00:36:09,160 --> 00:36:10,420
for taking care of him.

878
00:36:10,640 --> 00:36:12,320
As a result, he built great relationships with the neighbors,

879
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:14,080
and even became like their family member.

880
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:14,920
Li Jianjian's family

881
00:36:14,920 --> 00:36:16,380
made a lot of money from it.

882
00:36:16,960 --> 00:36:17,680
Yes.

883
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:19,360
So you can rest assured that

884
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,640
Ling Xiao and I will be great together.

885
00:36:20,640 --> 00:36:22,440
I'll definitely take good care of him.

886
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:24,640
Are you and Ling Xiao in a relationship?

887
00:36:24,680 --> 00:36:25,840
Yes, we are.

888
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:28,320
But Ling Xiao hasn't been back for long.

889
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,120
Did you start the relationship

890
00:36:29,120 --> 00:36:30,360
before he came back?

891
00:36:30,560 --> 00:36:31,320
No, no, no.

892
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,200
We started seeing each other

893
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,530
only after he came back.

894
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:35,520
I liked him when I was little.

895
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,120
Actually, Ling Xiao

896
00:36:37,120 --> 00:36:38,360
liked you as well.

897
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,760
I remember during summer holidays,

898
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,480
he'd come to our place to visit his grandmother,

899
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:43,440
but he never stayed more than one night.

900
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,360
He'd

901
00:36:44,360 --> 00:36:45,040
call your name

902
00:36:45,040 --> 00:36:45,880
all the time,

903
00:36:46,040 --> 00:36:47,120
and save all the goodies

904
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:48,400
for you.

905
00:36:51,520 --> 00:36:52,240
Jianjian,

906
00:36:52,240 --> 00:36:54,570
I don't want to waste too much of your time.

907
00:36:55,640 --> 00:36:56,520
OK, OK.

908
00:36:56,680 --> 00:36:57,720
If you need any help,

909
00:36:57,720 --> 00:36:59,050
feel free to let me know.

910
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,080
OK.

911
00:37:10,680 --> 00:37:11,810
What were you doing?

912
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:13,800
Nothing.

913
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:16,040
I just didn't want to bother her.

914
00:37:55,960 --> 00:37:59,000
Ling Xiao, what brought you back?

915
00:38:03,360 --> 00:38:04,420
They're in my flat?

916
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:07,210
Stay here, don't come over.

917
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:17,640
Why are you back?

918
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,080
You haven't seen your aunt

919
00:38:19,080 --> 00:38:20,610
for quite a years, have you?

920
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:21,880
Last time you met was 4 years ago

921
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,960
when you visited us

922
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,240
in Singapore, right?

923
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:24,800
Exactly.

924
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:26,680
What did you say to Jianjian?

925
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:30,220
I'm asking you what you said to Jianjian.

926
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:32,040
I didn't say anything.

927
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:33,960
What did she tell you?

928
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:35,080
She didn't say anything.

929
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:36,360
But I have eyes!

930
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:37,600
Ling Xiao,

931
00:38:37,600 --> 00:38:39,320
