932
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:41,520
Whatever you want to say, say it nicely.

933
00:38:42,520 --> 00:38:44,440
You can do whatever you want

934
00:38:44,440 --> 00:38:45,920
with Chengzi and me,

935
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,930
because you're our mom.

936
00:38:48,120 --> 00:38:49,160
But you can't insult Jianjian.

937
00:38:49,160 --> 00:38:50,440
Not a single word!

938
00:38:55,040 --> 00:38:55,680
Damn it.

939
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:02,200
Ling Xiao.

940
00:39:02,200 --> 00:39:03,660
It's a misunderstanding.

941
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:05,860
It's a misunderstanding.

942
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:07,720
Li Jianjian,

943
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:10,200
what did you say to Ling Xiao?

944
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:15,560
Tell me right now.

945
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:18,970
Did I do anything to you?

946
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:24,440
No, your mom didn't do anything to me.

947
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,240
I was upset with something else.

948
00:39:25,240 --> 00:39:26,570
I know you don't like me.

949
00:39:27,480 --> 00:39:28,600
But please stop

950
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:29,320
stirring things up

951
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,120
between me and my son.

952
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:31,380
Stop making things up.

953
00:39:32,680 --> 00:39:34,080
I know you don't like her.

954
00:39:35,880 --> 00:39:36,600
She's made you tea

955
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:37,520
and prepared fruit for you.

956
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:38,850
I saw her crying at home.

957
00:39:38,920 --> 00:39:40,480
Can you say it has nothing to do with you?

958
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:41,240
Ling Xiao,

959
00:39:41,240 --> 00:39:42,840
that's what your mom is like.

960
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:44,200
Although her words may be a bit harsh,

961
00:39:44,200 --> 00:39:46,330
she doesn't hold grudges in her heart.

962
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:49,760
I don't care how she feels

963
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:50,440
in her heart.

964
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,200
I don't want to know.

965
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:55,780
But I know what you think deep down in your heart!

966
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,240
I know you hate me.

967
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:01,440
I know nothing I do is right.

968
00:40:01,680 --> 00:40:02,600
You just want me to stay away from you

969
00:40:02,600 --> 00:40:03,880
as far as possible.

970
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:05,920
Why have I never seen you speak for

971
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:07,800
your younger sister like this?

972
00:40:08,720 --> 00:40:09,440
If you ever

973
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:10,560
treated your younger sister

974
00:40:10,560 --> 00:40:12,160
like you treat Li Jianjian even half,

975
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:13,080
she wouldn't

976
00:40:13,080 --> 00:40:14,080
have been

977
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:15,680
so rebellious.

978
00:40:20,040 --> 00:40:23,440
Fine. It's all my fault.

979
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:25,760
You're happy?

980
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,330
It's not your fault.

981
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,400
It's all my fault.

982
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:34,360
There's nothing wrong with you for hating your own mom.

983
00:40:34,360 --> 00:40:35,400
You only care about

984
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:36,560
your dad

985
00:40:36,560 --> 00:40:37,880
and your neighbors.

986
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,680
Because they care about me, too.

987
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:45,900
Why have you never cared about me?

988
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:02,040
Aunt,

989
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:03,800
sorry to

990
00:41:03,800 --> 00:41:04,600
get you involved

991
00:41:04,600 --> 00:41:05,330
in our fight.

992
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:08,540
Thanks for coming to help.

993
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,320
No problem, it's my pleasure.

994
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:12,000
Don't be mad with your mom.

995
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:15,480
I'm really sorry.

996
00:41:17,720 --> 00:41:18,760
Ling Xiao!
